This distribution includes the following components:

Protocol Implementation (protocol/)
  - Cryptographic primitives (BLAKE3, Ed25519)
  - Merkle tree implementations
  - Sparse Merkle Tree (SMT) structures
  - Canonicalization pipeline
  - Zero-knowledge proof protocols

Storage Layer (storage/)
  - PostgreSQL persistence layer
  - Protocol state management
  - Operational state management

API Gateway (api/)
  - FastAPI-based REST API
  - Ingestion and verification endpoints
  - Federation health monitoring

Debug UI (ui/)
  - Developer console
  - Proof inspection tools
  - Circuit constraint visualization

Zero-Knowledge Circuits (proofs/)
  - Circom circuit definitions
  - Poseidon hash implementations
  - Groth16 proving system integration

Schemas (schemas/)
  - JSON schema definitions
  - Canonical data formats

Verification Tools (verifiers/)
  - CLI verification tools
  - Multi-language verifier implementations (Go, JavaScript, Rust)

Examples and Test Vectors (examples/, test_vectors/)
  - Reference implementations
  - Golden test artifacts
  - Integration examples

